===========================================
Contemporary Source Data Set (source-cont)
===========================================

Samples from contemporary publications mentioned by Louwen in the content of chronicle data set 2. This set is used as external data to compare to the possible copied and paraphrased text in chronicle data set 2 to determine if the style of the chronicle fragments is similar to the sources which Louwen lists.

While the sources mentioned by Louwen in the first ‘historical’ section of his chronicle are mostly books, this set is compiled of mixed media including both books, periodicals, newspapers, and the publications of local authorities. 

Aanspraak Aan Het Exercitie-Genootschap Pro Patria et Libertate Te Purmerende. Naa Deszelfs Tweede Openlyke Exercitie Op Den 12 July Ao. 1786, 1786.
Berigt wegens de receptie, en kort verblyf, van Syn Doorlugtige Hoogheid Willem den Vyfde. P. Jordaan, 1773.
Berkhey, Joannes Le Francq van. Natuurlyke historie van Holland. Vol. 1. 9 vols. Amsterdam: Yntema en Tieboel, 1769. https://www.dbnl.org/tekst/fran011natu00_01/.
